message.body: Hello!
Hi. How are you today?
I'm good! How are you?
Pretty good. I'm starting my Sunday routine of cooking cleaning and getting caught up on tasks.
How about you? What are you up to today?
I'm going to see a movie with my dad for Father's Day. We're seeing man of steel have you seen it?
Nope. I'm not much of a movie fan. I almost forgot today is father's day! I guess i should start making some calls.
Hello! Sorry I wasn't able to talk much before, doing stuff with the family. How was your day?
It went pretty good. I just got home from church. There was a special service for father's day. How was your day with your family?
It was nice made some steak for my dad
Sounds delicious. Did he like it?
Yeah he did, he loves steak, and spending time with me and my sister
That's awesome. Sounds like he had a great father's day. What are your plans for the week?
I don't have much plans for this week, I'm trying to find a new apartment so I will hopefully be looking at a few places. How about you?
I hope you find a place you like. I'm going to go to rehearsals for a show that i'll be in this weekend.
Oh fun what show? Is it a play?
No it's a dance show.
Ooh what kind of dance I used to do ballet when I was younger
I don't really know. I was invited to be a part of a flash mob show and i agreed to do it. I don't even know what it means. Do you know what it is?

Ooh cool! hmm I think that's like when a group of people will randomly break out in a choreographed dance in a public place so one minute it will just bea normal day and the next people start dancing I think it'd be really cool to be in one!
Sounds fun! I look forward to it.
